title: Good App but...
comment: The basic functionality is done well, but it desperately needs username copying (they can be more complicated that the password for some websites that force alpha numeric passwords). Also there needs to be the ability to password protect the app itself in case some snatches your phone while its unlocked.
Great for ARMv6 or earlier phones that are not compatible with mobile Firefox, does exactly what it says.
I can't get it to work with my firefox sync account.
